.SH SIGNALS

.PP
.TP
SIGHUP 
reloads the zone and key sections in the configuration file and reloads the zone file(s) with incremented serial number, and close all log files and reopens them. 
.TP
SIGINT 
shutdowns the server 
.TP
SIGTERM 
(see SIGINT) 
